title: The Libertine
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A casual English style pub offers veg choices that include made-in-house seitan tacos and a roasted portobello sandwich. Several other dishes are vegetarian and could be made vegan upon request, such as the tex-med plate, Mediterranean plate, grilled cheese, Belgian tomato soup, jalapeno soup and mac 'n cheese. Hosts quarterly vegan beer dinners and meetups. Free Wi-Fi.
